Labo Car Designer is a great toy app for kids(3-5 years old) unleash their creativity by drawing their dream cars. 

[VIDEO]: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e3qj4gF0H8E 

All children have the same dream: build and driving their own cars. Labo Car Designer can make this dream come true. 


This app allows children to design(draw, customize and decorate) their own vehicles. 

- Features: 
1. Free to draw vehicles; 
2. Or follow tutorials to draw & color; 
3. 10 colors, 25 creativity and interesting tutorial vehicles; 
4. 14 exquisite tires, the size and spacing can be customized; 
5. 27 beautiful stickers and lights; 
6. Save vehicles to garage, unlimited; 
7. 15 fun-filled physical roads to explore, 4 weather modes, free to switch; 


