- Summary
A car design game that kids love to teach them how to draw vehicles. Labo Car Designer is a digital toy and a great preschool app. In the application,children can draw various vehicles,including construction vehicles,cars,trucks,fire engines,monster cars,big trucks,police cars,etc.,and can drive them to play. This game is suitable for boys from 3 years old and also suitable for girls from 3 years old.
